snippet: President Vladimir V. Putin of Russia and his Egyptian counterpart, Abdel Fattah el-Sisi, said Tuesday in Cairo that the two countries planned to jointly build Egypt’s first nuclear power plant.
lead_paragraph: President Vladimir V. Putin of Russia and his Egyptian counterpart, Abdel Fattah el-Sisi, said Tuesday in Cairo that the two countries planned to jointly build Egypt’s first nuclear power plant.

headline.main: Egypt: Putin Announces Plan to Help Build Nuclear Power Plant
headline.print_headline: Egypt: Putin Announces Plan to Help Build Nuclear Power Plant
